[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    181[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m  [38;2;191;97;106mThis is now the tenth consecutive recipe with this finding (2.4-2.10, 3.1, 3.2, 3.3, 3.4). The cookbook editor should treat the appendix-consolidation as the highest-leverage cookbook-wide editorial investment. For Recipe 3.4 specifically, the patient-safety stakes elevate the consequence of the doubled-counts to a level that warrants in-recipe discussion even if a cookbook-wide appendix is created.[K
