[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    188[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mProblem:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m No Dead Letter Queue or [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mOnFailure[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m destination is configured for any Lambda in the pipeline. The recipe's own "Why This Isn't Production-Ready" section names "Graceful degradation when dependencies fail" as a core production concern ("If the patient-context cache is unavailable, the pipeline has to fall back to something, because failing to dispense medications is a worse safety outcome than missing an anomaly check"), but the architectural artifacts that make a missed event detectable are not present.[K
