[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    401[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m  [38;2;191;97;106mThis is LOW because the note's protective framing ("does not constitute proof of diversion. Investigation to be conducted under existing pharmacy-compliance protocol") is exactly the right discipline for an alert that may be subpoenaed in an HR or legal proceeding. The minor tightening would be in the source attribution.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    402[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mFix:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m Soften the source attribution slightly: "Pattern matches diversion indicators consistent with ASHP guidance and common production detection patterns; does not constitute proof of diversion. Investigation to be conducted under existing pharmacy-compliance protocol with HR and legal involvement as appropriate." The "common production detection patterns" framing acknowledges that real systems combine multiple sources rather than implementing ASHP indicators verbatim.[K
