[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    416[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mPattern: A5 (severity "investigation" tier undefined) is a teaching-fidelity issue similar in shape to Recipe 3.1's diagram-vs-walkthrough findings.[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;192;197;206m The sample output uses a severity value that doesn't appear in the prose-defined hierarchy or the routing-pseudocode comparison logic. The fix is the smaller editorial change (define the tier explicitly) and aligns the sample output with the architectural framing.[K
